  "title": "Staff Nurse ( Surgery Clinic ) – Training Provided for OT Experience #HVN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong>:</p><p>·        To assist the doctors in the consultation room during clinic session</p><p>·        To provide health advice to patients / family</p><p>·        To explain to patient the scheme of payments and charges as necessary</p><p>·        To participate in quality management and work improvement discussions on nursing care rendered to patients</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>·        Registered with Singapore Nursing Board</p><p>·        Min 2 Years’ Experience as a Staff Nurse</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
